- **Build gate:** `michaelwegter.com` `npm run build` PASS (46 modules, 5.7s). `workSamples.js` entry id:11 valid (slug, `href → demos/ks-global-estates/`, screenshot path, tags).
- **Deploy is real:** local HEAD `e3b7e2c` == `origin/main` `e3b7e2c`, **0 ahead / 0 behind** — the demo + the sky-image fix are both on the remote. Pages auto-deploy trusted (not pollable here, per env). No backend needed (mock DB satisfies R1, as the brief requests); nothing to push in mw-backend.
- **Cover letter:** Michael's voice, 340 words, demo link in paragraph 2, all 11 requirements woven in naturally (no checklist), correct handle `github.com/mwegter95`, no em/en dashes.
- **One-pager:** renders with 0 page errors, all 5 media images load (hero + 3 stills, natural dims valid), full R1–R11 requirements matrix present, bespoke luxury design (not the michaelwegter.com look), no dashes.
- **Deck (deck.pptx):** 8 slides, 4 images embedded, demo link on slides 4 & 8, correct handle, **fully clean of em/en dashes across all XML** (slides + notes).
- **Images:** image-eval PASS — 25 unique property images verified by source metadata (22 Unsplash residential-property provenance + 3 LoremFlickr keyword-checked), one accepted gallery-only risk, no cityscapes. R10 satisfied.

